    - Invokes both:\n      - `loadPlugin(String, String)`\n      - `loadPlugin$default(...)`\n    - Verifies both instantiate `JvmMockKAgentFactory`.\n\nWhy this was needed:\n- `loadPlugin` is `inline` with a `reified` type parameter.\n- Normal Kotlin calls are inlined into the test class, so the dynamic-access frame is no longer `InternalPlatform.loadPlugin`.\n- Direct reflective calls to the JVM stub fail before the reflection call sites because Kotlin’s reified marker throws.\n- The patched loader removes only that guard so the published method body’s `Class.forName`, `getDeclaredConstructor`, and `newInstance` bytecode can execute with the original `InternalPlatform.kt` stack frames.\n\nAlso updated:\n- `tests/src/io.mockk/mockk-jvm/1.14.9/build.gradle`\n  - Added `org.ow2.asm:asm-tree:9.7.1` for the small bytecode patch helper.\n\nNative Image handling:\n- The dynamic class-loading path is wrapped with `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)` as required for behavior that depends on defining class bytecode at runtime.\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_087957684410c0260169fadc8f4798819cb8063a45390702ac\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1184, "output": 1208, "cacheRead": 71680, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 74072, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778048129538, "responseId": "resp_087957684410c0260169fadc828294819ca2b0b3a8d9ddb27f"}}
